Coldwell Banker Sea Coast Advantage - Jacksonville

data.description: Welcome Home! This Beautiful well maintained home is like NEW! This lovely home welcomes you with Foyer and LVP Flooring throughout main level. Open floor plan with Formal Dining room, Breakfast Nook, Kitchen with Center Island and an enormous Family Room with cozy Electric Fireplace. The Kitchen has Granite Countertops, Castled Cabinets and a Walk-In Pantry. Primary on upper level with Tray Ceiling along with other bedrooms all containing Walk-In closets as well. The ensuite has Dual Vanity sinks and a Separate Tub/Shower. Plenty of space for entertaining with a Screened in Patio and a large Deck with a Fenced in backyard. The home is also upgraded with Google Nest Smart Thermostats. Make this Milan Floorplan your home TODAY!
